1. *Knjiga* je puna zanimljivih priča. (The book is full of interesting stories.)
2. On voli da čita *knjigu* pre spavanja. (He likes to read the book before going to sleep.)
3. Učenik je odlučio da kupi novu *knjigu*. (The student decided to buy a new book.)
4. *Knjigama* se može mnogo naučiti. (You can learn a lot from books.)
5. Ona je imala mnogo *knjiga* na polici. (She had a lot of books on the shelf.)
6. U knjižari možete naći mnoštvo *knjiga*. (You can find a lot of books in the bookshop.)